flowchart TB
    X["x<br/>64 x 15 x 15"] --> SPLIT{"split"}

    SPLIT -->|learned update F of x| C1["Conv 3 x 3<br/>64 -> 64<br/>padding = 1"]
    C1 --> BN1["BatchNorm<br/>ReLU"]
    BN1 --> C2["Conv 3 x 3<br/>64 -> 64<br/>padding = 1"]
    C2 --> BN2["BatchNorm"]
    BN2 --> ADD(("add<br/>x + F(x)"))

    SPLIT -->|identity skip path<br/>unchanged x| ADD
    ADD --> RELU["ReLU"]
    RELU --> Y["block output<br/>64 x 15 x 15"]

